sections.heading: to 5-6-5 - Repealed.
sections.text: Repeals.— Laws 1993, ch. 181, § 1 repealed 5-6-1 through 5-6-5 NMSA 1978, as enacted by Laws 1861, p. 30, §§ 1 and 2, Laws 1869, ch. 32, §§ 14 and 15, and Laws 1963, ch. 142, § 1, regulating dances, effective June 18, 1993. For provisions of former sections,seethe 1992 NMSA 1978 onNMOneSource.com.
